          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The energy spectrum and polarization of photoneutrons",
                " from Be-9  at  135  degrees  at  the  bremsstrahlung",
                " endpoint  energy  =  85  MeV  were measured.  It was",
                " shown,  that the high value of the  polarization  of",
                " the photoneutrons with energy greater than 1 MeV and",
                " less than 3 MeV cannot  be  explained  only  by  the",
                " contribution  of  the  Be-9 valence neutron.  It was",
                " concluded that there is a noticeable contribution to",
                " the   polarization  from  neutrons  emitted  in  the",
                " processes involving the Be-9 core."
              ]
            }
          ],
